whole_object: When I said I was 'streamlining my commute,' I didn't expect to be teleported into a sci-fi movie tunnel!
single_object:
- Moving walkway: "I tried to walk on the moving walkway, but it just kept taking me for a ride!"  
- Tunnel: "This tunnel is so long, I half expected to find a lost civilization at the other end!"
